{"tid":607157,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老]各位有冇受過咩廢老嘅氣？","createTime":"2018-03-27T05:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T05:45:19.000Z","uid":88309,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1f43ce814679fcde87d94d2125054e9ff33746","tid":607157,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"先拋磚，各位都一齊講吓受過咩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過坐輕鐵成手拎住一大咋文件，有個廢老遲我一個站衝上車坐咗兩個站，明明本身架車已經勁多位佢行，我又冇阻住佢落車個位，佢落車嗰一吓仲要大大力推咗我一吓，幾乎成個企唔穩，佢仲要啤住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我唔明點解啲廢老依家會咁，我又冇諗住同你爭位坐，已經專登搵個位唔阻人都要推我一吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話點解唔現場屌佢嗰啲我先講一講，現場太多廢老，佢又唔出聲先，後生主動出聲先一定俾其他廢老屌，條廢老一定會扮可憐，結果點都會俾人話後生嘅蝦佢<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知上黎講都冇用，但係各位如果屋企有老人家咁做嘅不妨幫手話吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我祝全部仆街廢老長命百歲，百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f582bfb01348943d5f2e4eae0aa895d0d66517","tid":607157,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"有時會無屌返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe74ef28c0f1905cc3f543edc26ea91af7910593","tid":607157,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"eb87a000e0ee8b9ccf8c9a2d864ef5873d88a4c4","tid":607157,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f582bfb01348943d5f2e4eae0aa895d0d66517","tid":607157,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"有時會無屌返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"我都想，因為附近幾個後生都見到佢推我，但係我出聲肯定唔會幫口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866f89be694dd1548b28ff416a5d03e34f3c3ec4","tid":607157,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe74ef28c0f1905cc3f543edc26ea91af7910593","tid":607157,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"我認我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}